mify-woo-commerce-product-filter\">5. Themify &#8211; WooCommerce Product Filter</a></li><li><a href=\"#5-filter-everything-product-filter-word-press-filter\">6. Filter Everything — Product Filter &amp; WordPress Filter</a></li><li><a href=\"#6-wcapf-woo-commerce-ajax-product-filter\">7. WCAPF – WooCommerce Ajax Product Filter</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#conclusion\">Conclusion</a></li></ul></nav></div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"best-free-woo-commerce-product-filter-plugins\">Best Free WooCommerce Product Filter Plugins</h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"1-husky-products-filter-professional-for-woo-commerce\">1. Husky &#8211; Products Filter Professional for WooCommerce</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"332\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Husky-1-1024x332.png\" alt=\"HUSKY - Best Free WooCommerce Product Filter Plugins\" class=\"wp-image-11576\" title=\"5+ Best Free WooCommerce Product Filter Plugins 1\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Husky-1-1024x332.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Husky-1-300x97.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Husky-1-768x249.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Husky-1-1536x497.png 1536w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Husky-1.png 1544w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>HUSKY – WooCommerce Products Filter Professional</strong> is one of the best free WooCommerce product filter plugins designed to enhance product searches on WooCommerce stores. It allows customers to filter products easily by categories, attributes, prices, and more, offering a seamless and efficient shopping experience. Whether you run a small shop or a large marketplace, HUSKY adapts to your needs, making it an essential tool for improving user experience and boosting sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>SEO-friendly links create search-engine-optimized links for better Google rankings.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The filter form front builder allows you to build and customize filters directly on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>AJAX filtering ensures smooth, reload-free product filtering for faster results.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Dynamic product counts display available product counts.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Metadata and SKU filtering enable filtering of products by custom fields, SKU, and price.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Customizable design allows you to tailor filter elements to match your store&#8217;s look.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Step-by-step filtering guides customers through a step-by-step product selection process.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Infinite scrolling provides continuous product loading for a better browsing experience.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Products messenger notifies customers when their desired products become available.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Compatibility with the latest WooCommerce, popular themes, and PHP versions.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-products-filter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download</a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"2\">2. YITH WooCommerce Ajax Product Filter</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"330\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/YITHWooCommerce-1024x330.gif\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Ajax Product Filter -  Best Free WooCommerce Product Filter Plugins\" class=\"wp-image-11828\" title=\"5+ Best Free WooCommerce Product Filter Plugins 2\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/YITHWooCommerce-1024x330.gif 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/YITHWooCommerce-300x97.gif 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/YITHWooCommerce-768x248.gif 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>YITH WooCommerce Ajax Product Filter</strong> is one of the best free WooCommerce product filter plugins. It enables customers to find and filter products based on categories, tags, attributes, etc. This plugin ensures seamless navigation with unlimited presets and customizable options, boosting customer satisfaction and conversion rates.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Create and customize unlimited filter presets for different pages.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Display filters using widgets, shortcodes, or Gutenberg blocks.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Filter products by categories, tags, and attributes like size, color, and material.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Choose filter styles: checkboxes, select menus, text, and color swatches.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Adaptive filtering to hide unavailable terms dynamically.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Include a &#8220;Reset Filters&#8221; button for quick navigation.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Mobile-friendly scroll-to-top option.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SEO options to manage URL indexing.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Modern, performance-optimized design with lazy load functionality.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ajax-navigation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download</a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"2-advanced-ajax-product-filters\">3. Advanced AJAX Product Filters</h4>\n\n\n\n