sy to choose Elementor addons from the wide range of options available, we have listed some of the best free Elementor addons for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-rank-math-toc-block\" id=\"rank-math-toc\"><h2>Table of Contents</h2><nav><ul><li><a href=\"#what-are-elementor-addons\">What are Elementor addons?</a></li><li><a href=\"#best-free-elementor-addons-for-word-press\">Best Free Elementor Addons for WordPress</a><ul><li><a href=\"#1-essential-addons-for-elementor\">1. Essential Addons For Elementor</a></li><li><a href=\"#2-elementor-header-footer-builder\">2. Elementor Header &amp; Footer Builder</a></li><li><a href=\"#3\">3. Wbcom Essential Elementor</a></li><li><a href=\"#3-elements-kit-elementor-addons\">4. ElementsKit Elementor Addons</a></li><li><a href=\"#4-premium-addons-for-elementor\">5. Premium Addons for Elementor</a></li><li><a href=\"#5-happy-addons-for-elementor\">6. Happy Addons for Elementor</a></li><li><a href=\"#6-prime-slider\">7. Prime Slider</a></li><li><a href=\"#7-met-form\">8. MetForm</a></li><li><a href=\"#8-skyboot-custom-icons-for-elementor\">9. Skyboot Custom Icons for Elementor</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#conclusion\">Conclusion</a></li></ul></nav></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"what-are-elementor-addons\">What are Elementor addons?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Elementor Addons are plugins or extensions that enhance the functionality of the Elementor page builder, a widely-used WordPress plugin for creating custom website designs using a visual, drag-and-drop interface. These addons provide widgets, templates, features, and design options not included in the core Elementor plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below are some common features of Elementor Addons:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Additional Widgets:</strong> Addons often include new widgets that you can use in your Elementor designs, such as advanced forms, sliders, pricing tables, countdown timers, and more.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>&nbsp;Pre-made Templates:</strong> Many addons come with various pre-designed templates and blocks that can be easily imported and customized to speed up the design process.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>&nbsp;Enhanced Features:</strong> Addons can provide advanced features such as animations, custom post types, dynamic content integration, WooCommerce compatibility, and enhanced responsive design options.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Styling and Design Options</strong>: Addons offer more styling and customization options, allowing users to create more unique and visually appealing designs.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Performance Optimization:</strong> Some addons include tools to help optimize the performance of your Elementor designs, ensuring fast load times and better user experience.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"best-free-elementor-addons-for-word-press\"><strong>Best Free Elementor Addons for WordPress</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"1-essential-addons-for-elementor\">1. <strong>Essential Addons For Elementor</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"332\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/EssentialAddons-2-1024x332.gif\" alt=\"Essential Addons - Best Free Elementor Addons for WordPress\n\" class=\"wp-image-11327\" title=\"8+ Best Free Elementor Addons for WordPress in 2024 44\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/EssentialAddons-2-1024x332.gif 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/EssentialAddons-2-300x97.gif 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/EssentialAddons-2-768x249.gif 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/EssentialA